data.description: Contract Pending. Welcome to 5301 W. Saint Paul Ave in the heart of NW Lincoln! This stunning 1996 split-level home is set on a massive 12,800 SF corner lot, offering a blend of space & convenience. The impressive horseshoe-style driveway provides ample parking for all your guests, Step inside & be captivated by the bright, airy ambiance that flows through the open floor plan. The kitchen, adorned w/beautiful oak cabinetry is perfect for gathering loved ones. Host delightful dinner parties in the inviting informal dining rm, & unwind in the cozy living rm that basks in natural light pouring through the elegant bay window. Discover the comfort of the primary BR complete w/an ensuite bath, ideal for unwinding after a long day. 2 addt'l spacious BRs ensure everyone has their own sanctuary, while the full guest BA caters to all your family's needs. The expansive bsmt unveils a family/rec rm w/a charming wood-burning fireplace & a convenient 3rd BA.
